            a shape of a nervous face when looked at from the side. They are great all mountain boards that offer a taste
            of both rocker and camber boards. A rocker/camber board offers the control at slower speeds that a rocker board
            offers. They have some pop to them when taking jumps. They are a difficult to manage for beginners because
